   "source": [
    "# 🔍 Vision RAG System — BLIP + Open-Source VLMs + Gradio\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture:**\n",
    "- **BLIP** (`Salesforce/blip-image-captioning-large`) — auto-caption every uploaded image\n",
    "- **BLIP ITM** (`Salesforce/blip-itm-large-coco`) — cross-modal reranker (query ↔ image)\n",
    "- **CLIP** (`openai/clip-vit-base-patch32`) — dense visual embedding & ANN index\n",
    "- **FAISS** — fast approximate nearest-neighbour search\n",
    "- **LLaVA / InstructBLIP** — open-source VLM for answer generation\n",
    "- **Gradio** — interactive UI\n",
    "\n",
    "**Pipeline:**\n",
    "```\n",
    "Upload images → BLIP caption → CLIP embed → FAISS index\n",
    "        ↓ (query time)\n",
    "User query → CLIP embed → ANN top-N → BLIP ITM rerank → top-k → VLM → answer\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime:** Set to `GPU (T4)` in Runtime → Change runtime type"
   ]
  },
  {
